    • Method Detail

      • onResultReceived

        void onResultReceived(SearchResult result)
        This method is invoked each time when the status of the text search initiated by invoking the Browser.findText(SearchParams, SearchResultCallback) method on the loaded web page is updated. If the search is not interrupted and completes, this method will be invoked the last time with the result object, that has the SearchResult.isCompleted set to true. The number how many times this method will be invoked during one search is not defined and depends on the speed the Chromium engine is able process this search with.
        每次在加载的网页上调用Browser.findText（SearchParams，SearchResultCallback）方法启动的文本搜索状态更新时，都会调用此方法。如果搜索没有中断并完成，则最后一次将使用SearchResult.isCompleted设置为true的结果对象调用此方法。没有定义在一次搜索期间将调用该方法多少次的次数，并且取决于Chromium引擎处理该搜索的速度。
        Parameters:
        result - contains information about search result, such as a number of matches, index of the currently highlighted and selected match, and whether the search is completed. -包含有关搜索结果的信息，例如匹配数，当前突出显示和所选匹配项的索引以及搜索是否完成。
